	<h1 class="title">这几个 80 后技术宅改变了国内音乐视频行业</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1091/small/1091.jpg?1416973319" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">何姗</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-03-29 10:42:36 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/7870/medium/7870.JPG?1436694359" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


